name: Unidentified_Bith_musician_(concert_solo)
content: An unidentified Bith musician performed a series of concerts on the planet Coruscant during the Clone Wars, playing a wind instrument similar to a kloo horn. A series of posters were put up around Galactic City in order to promote the Bith's concerts. Hover taxi advertisements were also used to attract people. The Aurebesh caption, featured on posters and hover taxis alike, read "concert solo." After the war ended, the same poster appeared in Ord Mantell City on the planet Ord Mantell, indicating that the musician performed there as well. Several years later, when Ezra Bridger visited the Lothal Jedi Temple, he had a vision of his quarters aboard the Ghost, where the poster was lying on the floor. It was also lying there later, when Bridger entered his quarters for real.
